title: Beautiful 1 Bedroom Apartment in Art Deco Building on Capitol Hill!
map_address: 1743 Boylston Avenue near E. Howell Street
posting_body: ['Beautiful apartment in 1925 mission-style Art Deco building, renovated into 14 modern units.', ' Located at 1743 Boylston Avenue on Capitol Hill (with a walk score of 98%), it is convenient to both Broadway and downtown.', ' Nearby buses to city center, the U District, Northgate, and Redmond.', ' This beautiful one bedroom unit is a must-see!', ' It faces east and has a spacious layout, 9 ft. ceilings, large windows, and good light.', ' Wood cabinets/trim and tile floor in the kitchen, as well as a dishwasher, disposal, and microwave.', ' Intercom entry.', ' Cable and internet ready.', ' Laundry room on premises.', ' Sorry, no pets.', ' Call the manager at', 'show contact info', 'with questions or to schedule a viewing of this great apartment.', ' And for more pictures, visit <URL> and click on The Mission Inn.']
